texts.text: *Shriek*
Got it!
There's more coming, Honey!
*Hiss*
Shit... Yo, there's too many.
Hey, can one of you come and help us?!
No! Rika and I have our hands full as it is!
Sorry, we're not any better off!
We're seriously in trouble here!
Gakuto and I are in a bind too...! But give a second...!
Gakuto, please handle them!
Shiang Sun, what are you getting out your computer for!
Ririn... Head to the station!
Jeng Yun, please try to hold your ground!
You'll see each other soon!
Alright! Thanks, Shiang Sun!
We're spread too thin.
But I guess it's hard to avoid with this many demons appearing all at once.
And a huge disaster to top it all off! Got ya!
*Howl*
It looks like the only pit that took some people with it was that one.
The one Newbie jumped into?
And it looks like the demons are all comin' out of there too,
but we ain't investigatin' any time soon at this rate yo...
>*Boom*
The hell was that?!
It came from over there. Let's go!
It's...
>A giant eight-headed snake is battling against two other demons!
Susano-o! Unforgivable! I will win once and for all!
I will devour Kushinada with you there to bear witness!
Orochi... Back for more, I see.
Ask and you shall receive.
Such insolence! Come and face me!
No, you will come and face me!

*Hiss*
Hmph!
>Orochi repels Kushinada's attack back towards her with its tail!
Ahhh...!
>Susano-o reaches out to Kushinada as she falls,
>and sends a gust of wind to reel her into his arms!
I... I'm sorry, Susano-o. Something's not right...
It feels more powerful than before.

*Hiss*
I am indeed more powerful!
I will devour you... And become even more powerful!
They're busy with their own fight...
The regular serpent demons came out of that place,
so what if something that huge also came out of it?
Yo, we gotta help 'em out.
Fightin' a demon that came out of there
could mean that they know somethin' yo.
Fine. Let's go.
...? Who are you?
If it is humans, you must leave at once!
Yo, we're the Liberators! Devil Downloaders!
Demon users...?
Mind if we help ya fight that giant snake?
We'll make sure not to get in the way yo.
What do you think, Susano-o?
Do as you please...
It does not matter how many come! Humans especially!

*Hiss*
Humans, the wench... I will devour them all!
>Meanwhile, in the underground labyrinth...
Devil Download!
*Hiss*
>Every demon that's appeared so far has been defeated.
It's alright now.
We can keep going.
You say that but...
This place is...! It's full of monsters!
The walls don't look like anything I've ever seen before either.
But we gotta keep go... Huh?
Something up ahead doesn't feel right...
>A pile of bricks and concrete blocks the way forward.
A dead end...?
We came all this way for nothin'?!
What the hell do we do?! This place is full of monsters!
Don't worry.
Leave the fighting to me.
Uh, I mean... Your weird powers are...
Well, I guess we'd already be dead if it weren't for you.
As long as you're okay with it then...
But at this rate... Should we turn back and find another way?
Wait, I think there's a way on the other side.
Can I get some help moving this rubble?
If we linger too long, we'll be killed before we know it.
Yeah, okay. I'll help.
I wanna get out of here as fast as possible too.
But we need a better way to communicate than just callin' everyone, "you".
How's about we at least tell each other our names.
I'm Tatsuya. My last name's kinda weird so let's just leave it at that.
Umm... I'm Hayato...
Oh... I'm Hazuki.
I'm Kasuga...
(Tell them your name.)
Then let's get to work.
If anyone gets hurt, please tell me.
I'm a licensed nurse.
I have some bandages and stuff in my bag so...
(I can't fight these monsters and can't really help move stuff...)
(I can't treat wounds or anything either... I can't do anything...)
(I just need to stay out of everyone's way. No one's said anything yet so...)
